1. Molim vas, *koristite* olovku da popunite ovaj obrazac. (Please *use* a pen to fill out this form.)
2. Kada *koristite* računar, ne zaboravite da ga redovno čistite. (When you *use* a computer, don't forget to clean it regularly.)
3. Da biste postigli bolje rezultate, *koristite* ovu kremu svako veče. (To achieve better results, *use* this cream every night.)
4. *Koristite* li često društvene mreže? (Do you *use* social media often?)
5. Na ovom sajtu, možete *koristiti* različite filtere da biste pronašli željeni proizvod. (On this website, you can *use* different filters to find the desired product.)
6. Ne *koristite* upaljač u blizini benzina. (Do not *use* a lighter near gasoline.)
7. Učiteljica nam je rekla da *koristimo* crvenu boju za naslov. (The teacher told us to *use* the color red for the title.)
8. Koliko ljudi *koristi* javni prevoz u Beogradu? (How many people *use* public transportation in Belgrade?)
9. Pokušajte da *koristite* manje plastike kako biste smanjili svoj ekološki otisak. (Try to *use* less plastic to reduce your ecological footprint.)
10. Kada *koristite* ovaj uređaj, budite oprezni da ne povredite sebe ili druge. (When you *use* this device, be careful not to harm yourself or others.)